item.title: Insolidarity & sn.ow.y - Dust Off That Analog [lofi/synthwave]
item.dc:creator: AnirudhKhanna
item.description:
oooh nice intro. I love that piano, and those crackles are nice. damm i love that hook, this is the chillest track i’ve ever listened to lol. I love the automations on this, it’s insane. The drums are perfect. I love the highpass automations you made. For that second hook, you should remove the tone on that bass. But that was sick tho. I think if the tone was remmoved, it would be much better. That is pretty much the only bad part, but damn this is amazing. I love the chill vibe here, it’s like a mix of Mome and Petit Biscuit. I love the lead, as well. Nice job!
